for 8th one tip. do not and i mean DO NOT ever approach the north east corner (there is a crystal formation i use as a landmark) eqtraders says you can get the gems for 8th off the burrowing wyverns in the wyvern caves. what they forgot is that Tristala, who is L63 or 66 (i forget =p ) guards those caves and is faster then sow. she is kos to all, even tho i have almost maxed cov faction.... *smoosh*  (train of thought bad here, the wyvern cave is in the north east corner =p )<br>
